<br>
YAWN.<br>
<br>
When a wiz gets to 60, and gets the bane spells, he becomes most wanted for those end encounters where the banes work.  And from the sounds of it, these spells will be dropping from mobs where you're most likely 60 if you're getting them.<br>
<br>
SO, I don't see this as helping wizard from 1-59, which is where the class needs to most work to be balanced.<br>
<br>
BZZT, try again please.<br>
